eventText: Petra sends request to change the app store name from DGVS-LL Kodierleitfaden to DGVS Leitlinien.
DGVS app server update is approved from Kiran.
DGVS Android app with Kodierleitfaden GL is sent to Vaclav for checking.
DGVS iOS app with Kodierleitfaden GL is sent to Vaclav for checking.
Sambhaji proposes 28Feb as online date for Kodierleitfaden guideline.
Constance sends a feedback  that the icon and splash screen is not updated. Sambhaji requests Neville, Harshit to change the icon and splash screen.
Vaclav puts DGVS app in the sprint.
Sambhaji requests Constance to directly contact Neville for changes.
Pranav sends the updated splash screen to programmers.
Constance acknowledges that the splash screens looks fine.
Programmers asks if TOC color is also to be changed. Constance says, Petra is on sick leave today and will help you asap when sheâ€™s back in the office
Constance sends the Tools TOC corrections to Neville.
Neville changed the Tools TOC colors. Constance approved the Tools TOC. She sends some more changes today.
Petra sends the Tools toc color code.
Constance sends the changes to Neville for typos.
Constance sends email to Piyush, Shrinath to update the DGVS app name to DGVS-Leitlinien
Neville sends email to Constance to download the server updates to see the changes.
Constance approved the DGVS server update for both GI-Blutung and Kodierleitfaden.
Constance gave decision to provide two server updates.

Server update of Kodierleitfaden is pushed in the online app. Neville has now informed Constance.
Sambhaji clarifies that we are not storing IP addresses of users. We can even show a popup for GA, when the app starts.
Sambhaji sends an video to constance to clarify the doubts on popup.
Sambhaji has told Constance that changing app name for iOS is not possible. We can change the app name for Android.
Constance informs that nothing to be done for Android app name on Google Play.
Julia is replying back to client on IP address anonymizations.
